      <para id="id27780776">
        <emphasis effect="underline">General Guidelines</emphasis>
      </para>
      <list id="id25362643" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
        <item>You must have a courteous tone at all times. No yelling, name-calling or accusatory tones. </item>
        <item>Pieces of the game should only be used for their designed purpose.</item>
        <item>Unsportsmanlike conduct will result in losing board game privileges for a week.</item>
        <item>All those who are playing a game are responsible for putting it back in its box and returning it to the yard duty supervisor.</item>
